<p data-start="833" data-end="873">It is Angular frontend component layout.</p>
<hr data-start="875" data-end="878">
<h2 data-start="880" data-end="894">⚠ Important</h2>
<p data-start="896" data-end="912">Right now it is:</p>
<p data-start="914" data-end="966">👉 Static content layout<br data-start="938" data-end="941">
👉 No Angular logic yet</p>
