"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;div&gt;</span><span>1. Sales Order</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;div&gt;</span><span>2. Materials Ready</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;div&gt;</span><span>3. Machine Scheduling</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;div&gt;</span><span>4. Production Start</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;div&gt;</span><span>5. Quality Check</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼg">&lt;/section&gt;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div><div class="flex w-full justify-end px-3 mt-1" data-code-block-feedback-row="true"></div></div></div></pre>
