<hr data-start="5316" data-end="5319">
<h2 data-start="5321" data-end="5344">📌 What This Changes</h2>
<h3 data-start="5346" data-end="5366">🎯 Hero becomes:</h3>
<p data-start="5367" data-end="5416">Odoo-style expressive headline + handwritten feel</p>
<h3 data-start="5418" data-end="5438">🎨 Feature Grid:</h3>
<p data-start="5439" data-end="5479">Icons + soft card look + hover animation</p>
<h3 data-start="5481" data-end="5506">🌀 Visual Background:</h3>
<p data-start="5507" data-end="5544">Soft wavy background (not plain gray)</p>
<h3 data-start="5546" data-end="5569">📊 Structured Flow:</h3>
<p data-start="5570" data-end="5609">How it works section becomes meaningful</p>
<hr data-start="5611" data-end="5614">
<h2 data-start="5616" data-end="5656">📌 Next Level Enhancements (Optional)</h2>
<p data-start="5658" data-end="5697">If you want it <strong data-start="5673" data-end="5696">even closer to Odoo</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="5699" data-end="5879">✔ SVG illustrations (curves, charts)<br data-start="5735" data-end="5738">
✔ Scroll reveal animations (fade/slide)<br data-start="5777" data-end="5780">
✔ Light micro-animations<br data-start="5804" data-end="5807">
