<p data-start="28" data-end="54">You don’t like it because:</p>
<ul data-start="56" data-end="214">
<li data-start="56" data-end="88">
<p data-start="58" data-end="88">It still looks template-like</p>
</li>
<li data-start="89" data-end="116">
<p data-start="91" data-end="116">Too centered and boring</p>
</li>
<li data-start="117" data-end="140">
<p data-start="119" data-end="140">No visual hierarchy</p>
</li>
<li data-start="141" data-end="166">
<p data-start="143" data-end="166">No strong personality</p>
</li>
<li data-start="167" data-end="214">
<p data-start="169" data-end="214">It doesn’t feel like a powerful ERP product</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="216" data-end="243">Let’s redesign it properly.</p>
<p data-start="245" data-end="332">We’ll go with a <strong data-start="261" data-end="306">strong SaaS + Industrial + Premium layout</strong>, not plain, not childish.</p>
<hr data-start="334" data-end="337">
<h1 data-start="339" data-end="371">🔥 NEW DIRECTION (Much Better)</h1>
<p data-start="373" data-end="384">Instead of:</p>
<p data-start="386" data-end="439">• 3 circles<br data-start="397" data-end="400">
• Centered layout<br data-start="417" data-end="420">
• Flat background</p>
<p data-start="441" data-end="455">We will build:</p>
<p data-start="457" data-end="598">✔ Split layout<br data-start="471" data-end="474">
✔ Dark gradient section<br data-start="497" data-end="500">
✔ Big strong headline<br data-start="521" data-end="524">
✔ Right-side layered UI mock<br data-start="552" data-end="555">
✔ Floating stats<br data-start="571" data-end="574">
✔ More premium feeling</p>
<hr data-start="600" data-end="603">
<h1 data-start="605" data-end="648">✅ Replace Entire Production Planning Page</h1>
