<hr data-start="88" data-end="91">
<h2 data-start="93" data-end="114">✅ What Is Good Now</h2>
<p data-start="116" data-end="307">✔ Strong headline hierarchy<br data-start="143" data-end="146">
✔ Nice purple gradient accent<br data-start="175" data-end="178">
✔ Clear left-right structure<br data-start="206" data-end="209">
✔ Stats below CTA is smart<br data-start="235" data-end="238">
✔ Dashboard mock adds visual weight<br data-start="273" data-end="276">
✔ Feels more SaaS than before</p>
<p data-start="309" data-end="347">This is 70–75% professional level now.</p>
<hr data-start="349" data-end="352">
<h2 data-start="354" data-end="386">🚨 What Is Still Slightly Off</h2>
<ol data-start="388" data-end="616">
<li data-start="388" data-end="430">
<p data-start="391" data-end="430">Background feels slightly dull / flat</p>
</li>
<li data-start="431" data-end="471">
<p data-start="434" data-end="471">Right dashboard card shadow is weak</p>
</li>
<li data-start="472" data-end="522">
<p data-start="475" data-end="522">Bottom-right beige glow looks slightly random</p>
</li>
<li data-start="523" data-end="561">
<p data-start="526" data-end="561">Stats spacing can be more premium</p>
</li>
<li data-start="562" data-end="616">
<p data-start="565" data-end="616">The page transition between sections feels abrupt</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="618" data-end="660">Nothing is wrong — but it’s not “wow” yet.</p>
<hr data-start="662" data-end="665">
<h1 data-start="667" data-end="711">🎯 Quick Improvements to Make It 90% Level</h1>
<h3 data-start="713" data-end="745">1️⃣ Improve Background Depth</h3>
<p data-start="747" data-end="798">Instead of single gradient, add subtle radial glow:</p>
