<hr data-start="374" data-end="377">
<h1 data-start="379" data-end="424">🎯 NEW QUALITY PAGE – DESIGN SHOWCASE STYLE</h1>
<p data-start="426" data-end="443">Design Direction:</p>
<p data-start="445" data-end="648">• Large split typography<br data-start="469" data-end="472">
• Soft gradient background (very subtle)<br data-start="512" data-end="515">
• Glass floating cards<br data-start="537" data-end="540">
• Asymmetric layout<br data-start="559" data-end="562">
• Visual rhythm (not stacked boring sections)<br data-start="607" data-end="610">
• Strong spacing<br data-start="626" data-end="629">
• Premium UI feel</p>
