n>  left: </span><span class="ͼb">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼd">card</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼd">small</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼd">right</span><span> {</span><br><span>  bottom: </span><span class="ͼb">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>  right: </span><span class="ͼb">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6">/* ================= MODULES SECTION ================= */</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼd">qa-modules</span><span> {</span><br><span>  padding: </span><span class="ͼb">120</span><span class="ͼ8">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼb">8</span><span class="ͼ8">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>  text-align: </span><span class="ͼb">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>  background: </span><span class="ͼb">white</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼd">qa-modules</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">h2</span><span> {</span><br><span>  font-size: </span><span class="ͼb">48</span><span class="ͼ8">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  margin-bottom: </span><span class="ͼb">70</span><span class="ͼ8">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  font-weight: </span><span class="ͼb">700</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼd">modules-grid</span><span> {</span><br><span>  display: </span><span class="ͼb">grid</span><span>;</span><br><span>  grid-template-columns: </span><span class="ͼ8">repeat</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼb">auto-fit</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼ8">minmax</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼb">260</span><span class="ͼ8">px</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼb">1</span><span class="ͼ8">fr</span><span>));</span><br><span>  gap: </span><span class="ͼb">40</span><span class="ͼ8">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼd">module</span><span> {</span><br><span>  padding: </span><span class="ͼb">35</span><span class="ͼ8">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  border-radius: </span><span class="ͼb">20</span><span class="ͼ8">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  background: #f7f8ff;</span><br><span>  transition: </span><span class="ͼb">0.3</span><span class="ͼ8">s</span><span> </span><span class="ͼb">ease</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼd">module</span><span>:</span><span class="ͼd">hover</span><span> {</span><br><span>  background: #eef1ff;</span><br><span>  transform: </span><span class="ͼ8">translateY</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼb">-8</span><span class="ͼ8">px</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼd">module</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">h3</span><span> {</span><br><span>  margin-bottom: </span><span class="ͼb">15</span><span class="ͼ8">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="4710" data-end="4713">
<h1 data-start="4715" data-end="4755">🔥 Why This Looks Like Design Showcase</h1>
<p data-start="4757" data-end="4952">✔ Big expressive typography<br data-start="4784" data-end="4787">
✔ Asymmetric floating layout<br data-start="4815" data-end="4818">
✔ Layered cards<br data-start="4833" data-end="4836">
✔ Clean modern gradient<br data-start="4859" data-end="4862">
✔ More visual depth<br data-start="4881" data-end="4884">
✔ Feels premium SaaS<br data-start="4904" data-end="4907">
✔ Completely different from production page</p>
<hr data-start="4954" data-end="4957">
<p data-start="4959" data-end="4980">Now tell me honestly:</p>
<p data-start="4982" data-end="5078" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Is this closer to what you want?<br data-start="5014" data-end="5017">
Or do you want even more bold / more creative / more minimal?</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span clas