   </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">class</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"quality-line"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼg">&lt;/section&gt;</span><br><br><br><span class="ͼg">&lt;section</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">class</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"qa-structure"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><br><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">class</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"qa-row"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">class</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"qa-number"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><span>01</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">class</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"qa-content"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;h2&gt;</span><span>Incoming Quality Control</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/h2&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;p&gt;</span><br><span>        Digitally validate raw materials before production begins.</span><br><span>        Eliminate downstream defects at the source.</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">class</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"qa-row"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">class</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"qa-number"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</spa