<p data-start="25" data-end="125">You don’t want blocks.<br>
You don’t want enterprise stiffness.<br>
You want personality + energy like Odoo.</p>
<p data-start="127" data-end="188">That handwritten, playful, bold hero.<br>
But still professional.</p>
<p data-start="190" data-end="249">Let’s build that style — adapted for Digizura (not copied).</p>
<hr data-start="251" data-end="254">
<h1 data-start="256" data-end="296">🎯 What Makes That Odoo Hero Powerful?</h1>
<p data-start="298" data-end="315">It works because:</p>
<p data-start="317" data-end="479">• Big expressive typography<br data-start="344" data-end="347">
• One highlighted phrase<br data-start="371" data-end="374">
• Hand-drawn accent<br data-start="393" data-end="396">
• Playful underline<br data-start="415" data-end="418">
• Simple background<br data-start="437" data-end="440">
• Strong CTA focus<br data-start="458" data-end="461">
• No heavy cards</p>
<p data-start="481" data-end="496">It feels alive.</p>
<p data-start="498" data-end="545">So we’ll create a Digizura version for Quality.</p>
<hr data-start="547" data-end="550">
<h1 data-start="552" data-end="605">🔥 New Creative Hero Concept (Odoo-Inspired Energy)</h1>
<p data-start="607" data-end="618">Instead of:</p>
<p data-start="620" data-end="649">"Quality Is Not Inspected In"</p>
<p data-start="651" data-end="666">We go stronger.</p>
<hr data-start="668" data-end="671">
<h2 data-start="673" data-end="704">✨ Hero Copy (Startup Energy)</h2>
<h3 data-start="706" data-end="729">Engineered Quality.</h3>
<h3 data-start="730" data-end="757">Built Into Every Meter.</h3>
<p data-start="759" data-end="810">With a brush-style highlight behind one key phrase.</p>
