<h1 data-start="3691" data-end="3714">🎯 What This Achieves</h1>
<p data-start="3716" data-end="3731">This now feels:</p>
<p data-start="3733" data-end="3876">✔ Startup-level modern<br data-start="3755" data-end="3758">
✔ Expressive<br data-start="3770" data-end="3773">
✔ Not boring ERP<br data-start="3789" data-end="3792">
✔ Clean light theme<br data-start="3811" data-end="3814">
✔ Confident<br data-start="3825" data-end="3828">
✔ Visually alive<br data-start="3844" data-end="3847">
✔ Inspired — but not copied</p>
<hr data-start="3878" data-end="3881">
<p data-start="3883" data-end="3925">If you want next level polish, we can add:</p>
<p data-start="3927" data-end="4091">• Animated text reveal<br data-start="3949" data-end="3952">
• Real SVG brush stroke instead of CSS highlight<br data-start="4000" data-end="4003">
• Subtle moving underline<br data-start="4028" data-end="4031">
• Section transition wave<br data-start="4056" data-end="4059">
• Product UI mockup below hero</p>
<p data-start="4093" data-end="4105">Now tell me:</p>
<p data-start="4107" data-end="4142">Do you want this page to feel more:</p>
<p data-start="4144" data-end="4212">Premium SaaS<br data-start="4156" data-end="4159">
