<p data-start="31" data-end="61">You’re right about two things:</p>
<ol data-start="63" data-end="186">
<li data-start="63" data-end="127">
<p data-start="66" data-end="127">Content feels too short → it needs more depth and authority</p>
</li>
<li data-start="128" data-end="186">
<p data-start="131" data-end="186">Heading style should not feel childish or handwritten</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="188" data-end="253">You’re building a manufacturing platform — not a creative agency.</p>
<p data-start="255" data-end="303">So we remove the playful brush vibe and make it:</p>
<p data-start="305" data-end="377">✔ Strong<br data-start="313" data-end="316">
✔ Structured<br data-start="328" data-end="331">
✔ Premium<br data-start="340" data-end="343">
✔ Clear value<br data-start="356" data-end="359">
✔ More substance</p>
<p data-start="379" data-end="430">No handwriting.<br>
No playful underline.<br>
Still modern.</p>
<hr data-start="432" data-end="435">
<h1 data-start="437" data-end="455">🔥 New Direction</h1>
<p data-start="457" data-end="468">Instead of:</p>
<p data-start="470" data-end="514">Engineered Quality<br data-start="488" data-end="491">
Built Into Every Meter.</p>
<p data-start="516" data-end="559">We make it stronger and more authoritative.</p>
