<h1 data-start="566" data-end="606">✅ Updated Hero Content (More Powerful)</h1>
<h3 data-start="608" data-end="642">Precision Quality Management</h3>
<h3 data-start="643" data-end="681">Across Your Entire Production Line</h3>
<p data-start="683" data-end="691">Subtext:</p>
<p data-start="693" data-end="877">Control inspections, enforce compliance standards, eliminate defects early, and maintain complete batch traceability — all from a single unified platform built for cable manufacturers.</p>
<p data-start="879" data-end="910">Now it sounds enterprise-ready.</p>
