e="assistant" data-message-id="5b67984c-2623-40c6-bde6-e76c46f64241" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="22">Okay. Stop everything.</p>
<p data-start="24" data-end="75">You’re saying <strong data-start="38" data-end="44">no</strong> because this still feels like:</p>
<p data-start="77" data-end="163">• Generic SaaS<br data-start="91" data-end="94">
• Corporate ERP<br data-start="109" data-end="112">
• Safe<br data-start="118" data-end="121">
• Boring<br data-start="129" data-end="132">
• Too structured<br data-start="148" data-end="151">
• No “wow”</p>
<p data-start="165" data-end="249">You want something that <strong data-start="189" data-end="207">feels designed</strong>.<br data-start="208" data-end="211">
Like Odoo — but powerful, not playful.</p>
<p data-start="251" data-end="284">Let’s rebuild this the right way.</p>
<hr data-start="286" data-end="289">
<h1 data-start="291" data-end="312">🎯 The Real Problem</h1>
<p data-start="314" data-end="341">Your page still feels like:</p>
<p data-start="343" data-end="386">Big heading<br data-start="354" data-end="357">
Paragraph<br data-start="366" data-end="369">
Buttons<br data-start="376" data-end="379">
Stats</p>
<p data-start="388" data-end="409">That pattern is dead.</p>
<p data-start="411" data-end="457">We need <strong data-start="419" data-end="456">visual drama + strong composition</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="459" data-end="462">
<h1 data-start="464" data-end="524">🔥 New Concept — Split Bold Layout (Design Showcase Style)</h1>
<p data-start="526" data-end="546">Instead of centered.</p>
<p data-start="548" data-end="554">We go:</p>
<p data-start="556" data-end="671">LEFT → Huge bold statement<br data-start="582" data-end="585">
RIGHT → Layered visual panel (overlapping shapes)<br data-start="634" data-end="637">
BOTTOM → Structured content band</p>
<p data-start="673" data-end="704">This will finally feel premium.</p>
<hr data-start="706" data-end="709">
<h1 data-start="711" data-end="745">💎 NEW DESIGN (Different Energy)</h1>
