<h1 data-start="3661" data-end="3690">🎯 Why This Feels Different</h1>
<p data-start="3692" data-end="3697">This:</p>
<p data-start="3699" data-end="3872">✔ Is not centered boring layout<br data-start="3730" data-end="3733">
✔ Has asymmetry<br data-start="3748" data-end="3751">
✔ Has overlapping shapes<br data-start="3775" data-end="3778">
✔ Has visual hierarchy<br data-start="3800" data-end="3803">
✔ Feels designed<br data-start="3819" data-end="3822">
✔ Feels startup-modern<br data-start="3844" data-end="3847">
✔ Still clean and light</p>
<p data-start="3874" data-end="3934">This finally feels like a homepage hero — not documentation.</p>
<hr data-start="3936" data-end="3939">
<p data-start="3941" data-end="3962">Now tell me honestly:</p>
<p data-start="3964" data-end="4003">Does THIS feel closer to what you want?</p>
