<hr data-start="2710" data-end="2713">
<h1 data-start="2715" data-end="2739">🎯 What This Gives You</h1>
<p data-start="2741" data-end="2906">✔ Handwritten big expressive heading<br data-start="2777" data-end="2780">
✔ Yellow paint highlight<br data-start="2804" data-end="2807">
✔ Centered playful layout<br data-start="2832" data-end="2835">
✔ Soft background<br data-start="2852" data-end="2855">
✔ Curved bottom shape<br data-start="2876" data-end="2879">
✔ Odoo-style landing feel</p>
