<h1 data-start="2681" data-end="2705">🔥 Now What You’ll See</h1>
<p data-start="2707" data-end="2840">✔ Real handwriting look<br data-start="2730" data-end="2733">
✔ Slight tilt paint stroke<br data-start="2759" data-end="2762">
✔ Clean buttons<br data-start="2777" data-end="2780">
✔ Soft Odoo background<br data-start="2802" data-end="2805">
