<hr data-start="2842" data-end="2845">
<p data-start="2847" data-end="2874">If you want it even closer:</p>
<ul data-start="2875" data-end="3024">
<li data-start="2875" data-end="2912">
<p data-start="2877" data-end="2912">I can add the blue underline stroke</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2913" data-end="2944">
