You don’t like that Caveat handwriting. It looks too soft / too playful.</p>
<p data-start="85" data-end="101">Odoo’s style is:</p>
<p data-start="103" data-end="194">• Bold<br data-start="109" data-end="112">
• Slightly imperfect<br data-start="132" data-end="135">
• Thick marker feel<br data-start="154" data-end="157">
• Not thin cursive<br data-start="175" data-end="178">
• Not childish</p>
<p data-start="196" data-end="295">So we change the handwriting to something closer to <strong data-start="248" data-end="277">thick marker / bold brush</strong>, not cute script.</p>
<hr data-start="297" data-end="300">
