<h1 data-start="1237" data-end="1259">🎯 My Recommendation</h1>
<p data-start="1261" data-end="1265">Use:</p>
<p data-start="1267" data-end="1290">👉 <strong data-start="1270" data-end="1290">Permanent Marker</strong></p>
