<hr data-start="3081" data-end="3084">
<h1 data-start="3086" data-end="3103">🔥 What Changed</h1>
<p data-start="3105" data-end="3145">Before:<br>
Flat white<br>
Box layout<br>
Basic text</p>
<p data-start="3147" data-end="3279">Now:<br>
• Soft gradient depth<br data-start="3173" data-end="3176">
• Huge faded “01” in background<br data-start="3207" data-end="3210">
• Elevated product card<br data-start="3233" data-end="3236">
• Layered visual depth<br data-start="3258" data-end="3261">
• Better spacing</p>
<p data-start="3281" data-end="3295">It feels like:</p>
<p data-start="3297" data-end="3344">Real SaaS<br>
Product showcase<br>
Premium landing page</p>
<p data-start="3346" data-end="3364">Not documentation.</p>
<hr data-start="3366" data-end="3369">
<p data-start="3371" data-end="3419">If you want to go one level higher, next we can:</p>
<p data-start="3421" data-end="3579">• Add animated floating cards<br data-start="3450" data-end="3453">
• Add scroll-triggered fade-in<br data-start="3483" data-end="3486">
• Add subtle grain texture<br data-start="3512" data-end="3515">
• Add asymmetric section break<br data-start="3545" data-end="3548">
• Add diagonal background cut</p>
<p data-start="3581" data-end="3589">Tell me:</p>
<p data-start="3591" data-end="3658">Do you want premium startup level<br data-start="3624" data-end="3627">
or enterprise industrial level?</p>
